    "body": "This adds variant `cxx_exceptions`, to the openmpi package. When on, this passes `--enable-cxx-exceptions` as a config argument to openmpi. The variant defaults to `True`. \r\n\r\nThis option avoids outright openmpi crashes when C++ MPI programs throw exceptions, and allows you to actually see c++ exception messages. \r\n \r\n\r\n",
